headline: Thompson Thrift's 100th Multifamily Community to be Developed in Atlanta Suburb
summary: Thompson Thrift, a full-service nationally recognized real estate company and one of the nation's leading multifamily developers, today announced that it will develop Lineage, a 300-unit multifamily community in Dacula, a suburb approximately 30 miles northeast of downtown Atlanta. Lineage marks Thompson Thrift's 100th multifamily community developed nationwide, a milestone reflecting the company's four decades of experience delivering resident focused communities in high growth markets.
